Ing '''Castila''' o '''Español''' metung yang [[Romance languages|amanung Romance]] a menibat king dake nang pangulu ning [[Spain|España]]. Iti ing opisial a amanu ning España ampo ning keraklan da reng bansa king [[w:Latin America|America Latina]], amo ning [[Equatorial Guinea]] king [[Africa]]. Miras lang adwang pulu’t limang bansa ampong teritoriu deng gagamit king Castila antimong manimunang amanu. Bukud kaniti, maulaga yang amanu kareng dakal pang lugal.  

Migumpisa ya ing Castila antimong dialectu ning [[Latin]] kareng mangalaut a salapungan kareng lalawigan ning [[Cantabria]], [[Burgos]], [[Soria]] and [[w:La Rioja (autonomous community)|La Rioja]]  king pangulu ning España. Manibat karin, bagya-bagya yang mikalat kilub ning Kayaryan ning [[Kayaryan ning Castilia|Castilia]], nung nu ya miyalkus (evolved) at king lambatan, meging manimunang amanu ning kapamahalan ampo ning kalakal. Midala ya king [[w:Americas|America]] at aliwa pang dake ning yatu karing tawling limang siglu (dilanwa) kapamilatan da reng colonista ampong talapaglakbeng Español.   

Miraras lang atlung dalan a milyun adwang pulu’t adwang miliun (400,000,000) anggang apat a ralan a milyun deng magsalitang king amanung iti.<ref name = "universidad de Mexico">[http://209.85.135.104/search?q=cache:v5IUdEETu40J:www.lllf.uam.es/~fmarcos/coloquio/Ponencias/MMelgar.doc+%22En+el+mundo+lo+hablan+aproximadamente+400+millones+de+personas%22+%22Adicionalmente+100+millones+de+personas+hablan+espa%C3%B1ol+como+segunda+lengua%22&hl=es&ct=clnk&cd=1&gl=es Universidad de México]</ref><ref name="instituto cervantes">Instituto Cervantes ([http://66.102.9.104/search?q=cache:0i7Y43lUanEJ:www.elmundo.es/elmundo/2007/04/26/cultura/1177610767.html+%22Instituto+Cervantes%22%22los+actuales+500+millones+de+hispanohablantes+en+Latinoam%C3%A9rica+y+Espa%C3%B1a%22&hl=es&ct=clnk&cd=2&gl=es "El Mundo" news])</ref>. Uli na niti, iti ing maragul diling amanung Romance, at mapalyaring ing kadwang pekamaragul a yamanu agpang king bilang da reng tubung magsalita. Ing tantya ra, nung piyabe la reng tubu ampong e tubung magsalita, miras lang limang dalan a miliun deti. Uli na niti, mapalyaring ing Castila ing kapat a pekamaragul a yamanu agpang king pangkabilugan a bilang da reng  talapagsalita.<ref name = "universidad de Mexico">[http://209.85.135.104/search?q=cache:v5IUdEETu40J:www.lllf.uam.es/~fmarcos/coloquio/Ponencias/MMelgar.doc+%22En+el+mundo+lo+hablan+aproximadamente+400+millones+de+personas%22+%22Adicionalmente+100+millones+de+personas+hablan+espa%C3%B1ol+como+segunda+lengua%22&hl=es&ct=clnk&cd=1&gl=es Universidad de México]</ref><ref name="instituto cervantes">Instituto Cervantes ([http://66.102.9.104/search?q=cache:0i7Y43lUanEJ:www.elmundo.es/elmundo/2007/04/26/cultura/1177610767.html+%22Instituto+Cervantes%22%22los+actuales+500+millones+de+hispanohablantes+en+Latinoam%C3%A9rica+y+Espa%C3%B1a%22&hl=es&ct=clnk&cd=2&gl=es "El Mundo" news]).</ref>

Metung ya kareng [[w:United Nations#Languages|anam a oficial a amanu king pamipalakad]] ning [[Misasanmetung a Bansa]] o United Nations. Dakal lang dili reng magsalita kaniti king [[Pangulung America]], [[Mawling America]], [[España]], at king mas malating bilang king [[Africa]] ampong [[w:Asia Pacific|Asia Pacifico]]. Ing Castila murin ing kadwang pekamaragul a yamanu king 
[[w:United States|America]]<ref>[https://www.cia.gov/cia/publications/factbook/geos/us.html CIA The World Factbook United States]</ref>, nung nu iti murin ing popular diling dayung amanu (foreign language) a panigaralan da kareng pipagaralan ampong universidad <ref>{{PDFlink|[http://www.census.gov/prod/2005pubs/06statab/pop.pdf United States Census Bureau]|1.86&nbsp;[[Mebibyte|MiB]]<!-- application/pdf, 1956553 bytes -->}}, Statistical Abstract of the United States: page 47: Table 47: Languages Spoken at Home by Language: 2003</ref><ref>{{PDFlink|[http://www.adfl.org/resources/enrollments.pdf Foreign Language Enrollments in United States Institutions of Higher Learning]|129&nbsp;[[Kibibyte|KiB]]<!-- application/pdf, 132628 bytes -->}}, MLA Fall 2002.</ref>

==Pamitinduk-tinduk (Classification)==
Malapit yang dili ing Castila kareng aliwang amanung Romance a [[w:West Iberian languages|Albugang Iberian]]: [[Asturian language|Asturian]] ({{lang|ast|''asturianu''}}), [[Galician language|Galician]] ({{lang|gl|''galego''}}), [[Ladino language|Ladino]] ({{lang|lad|''Djudeo-espanyol''}}, {{lang|lad|''sefardí''}}), and [[Portuguese language|Portuguese]] ({{lang|pt|''português''}}), at, kareng mapilang aspetu, king [[Aragonese language|Aragonese]] ({{lang|an|''aragonés''}}) ampong [[Catalan language|Catalan]] ({{lang|ca|''català''}}).

Ing Catalan, metung a amanung [[w:Iberian Romance languages|Aslagang Iberian]] (East Iberian), mas malapit ya ketang kasiping nang amanung [[w:Occitan language|Occitan]] ({{lang|oc|''occitan''}}) kesa king pamikamaganak da reng Castila (Español) ampong Portugues. Miwawangis la garalita (gramatica) deng Castila ampong Portugues, pati na ing keraklan da reng karelang amanu o vocabulariu, at metung a kasalesayan, particular king impluensiya ning Arabu, anyang sinakup deng Muslim ing keraklan ning peninsula (pareu lang melaganap kareng teritoriung Muslim deng adwa). Tatantyan dang 89% ing karelang pamiyawig. <ref name="ethnologue"/>

Ing Ladino naman, a keraklan ing Castila ketang panaun a medieval (Edad Media, Middle Ages o Kalibudtang Panaun), at mas malapit king makabayung Castila o Español kesa king sanu pa mang amanu, gagamitan de reng lahi da reng Judiung Sephardic, a mitabi king España ketang kalabing limang siglu o dilanwa (15th century). Agpang karing dakal nang kauryan, e ya aliwang amanu nun e metung ya mung dialectu ning Castila. Ala lu king Ladino deng katayang ibat kareng tubu king America (Indian o native American) a mikalat ketang panaun ning colonialismu. Atin yang kataya ibat king Turco, Hebreo at aliwa pang amanu da reng lugal nung nu la menuknangan deng Sephardi.


